        "username": "nasf",
        "inactive": true
      },
      "date": "2015-02-27 11:36:49.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review-1\n\nDuring soak test, we does not inject some failure stub, but the LFSCK repaired something unexpectedly, this patch is mainly used to cache what inconsistency the LFSCK found and repaired. It will not be landed to master.",
